Mike,

The Magical fuel flow / mpg meter's of the 70's were nothing more than
vacuum gauges---

Hammer down--vacuum drops so the does the needle and your fuel
economy---

This unmagical thing you could do to your Bus--No James Bond type thig
here-- very simple 

My 325 BMW has the same thing in the gauge cluster--and it is a
computerized to the max vehicle--but it still uses the  tried and true
vacuum gauge for the fuel economy / mpg read out.

